@node Main "Star_Q - Documentation"

                              'Star_Q' 1.12

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Star_Q' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} featuring 3 star-shaped boards. It is
based on the familiar 'Solo' or 'Hi-Q' type of game, the idea is simple:
you move a peg, over an other peg, either horizontally or diagonally, to
an empty space, the other peg is then removed from the board.

  The goal is to remove all the pegs, leaving only one on the board.
If you play the @{" Inverted " link play} game, you start with one peg and you try
to fill the board leaving only one empty space.

  Have fun!

